Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.45,0:00:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飘忽不定的罪孽之影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.22,0:00:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可悲的宿命 迷失的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因憎恨和被憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.96,0:00:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而破碎的两面镜子 是双重的枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在交错的时光与黑暗中浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的怨恨 替你消除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.37,0:02:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早马 继马 灶马
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.37,0:02:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(724,178)\frz-90\fn@方正隶变_GBK\fs30}「早馬」 快报使者用的快马
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.37,0:02:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(764,232)\frz-90\fn@方正隶变_GBK\fs30}「継馬」 因马匹疲惫紧急换乘用的马
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.37,0:02:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(804,110)\frz-90\fn@方正隶变_GBK\fs30}「竈馬」 即蟋蟀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马分各种各样的 也有不可饶恕的马
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你一样的野马
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs35}「野次馬」一语双关，指爱起哄的人之意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起码要给你送个行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这算是对“马”弹琴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.89,0:02:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是第五个了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:03:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V的惨剧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饭馆名 喜八
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚又出命案了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是第五个了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是咱们镇上的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店长觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无辜的人都被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还真是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 被杀总是有被杀理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 这话要被他家人听到了会遭怨恨的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 八百春
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说到怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说有个叫地狱通信的网站
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在上面输入怨恨的人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个叫地狱少女的孩子就会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮你消除无法消除的怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说这位是店长的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（情人）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我作为主治医师有这个责任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请尽快住院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您有工夫理会我这个风烛残年的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如替我女儿想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是久住喜八吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.82,0:05:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还真是条嘈杂的街啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(716,200)\frz-90\fn@方正隶变_GBK\fs30}由于最近这附近正在发生“连续\N杀人魔事件”，夜间单独行走、\N严锁房门等事须充分注意。另外\N若见到可疑人等，请告知最近的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(680,174)\frz-90\fn@方正隶变_GBK\fs30}警署、站岗警卫或派出所。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 哎呀 世风日下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们也开始工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就去调查牧村达彦这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去镇上调查情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要我来负责那个老头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 既然他开店的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是在这儿打工也挺省事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.19,0:06:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不错不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先来点喝的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个 两杯生啤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问您要点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可来了 真够慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎算了 先来杯生啤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人 您开车的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我们不能卖酒给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少罗嗦 拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说…客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了 快点拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你笑什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们他妈瞧不起人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么话可以冲我来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 来得好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是趁早住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么躲开的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你后面长眼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:07:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得有点过火了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差的远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店长还是老样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凡是有开车来的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他绝对不卖酒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出过那种事故的话也是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 那最里面的草席房间的桌子上摆着照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那已经是五年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为那场事故 店长的太太和儿子都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs35}椿是山茶花 菊里头上的也是这种花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有女儿小椿保住了一条性命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是五年过去了 至今神志不清
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说她是几乎不可能醒来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听八百春先生他们那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您的女儿叫小椿是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在你爸爸店里打工的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,废话就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧 这孩子已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么年轻漂亮的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能住这么阴暗的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是放弃了小椿姑娘就太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管医生怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 就算世人都说没希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作父亲的最少要坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身为人父就是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说的跟什么都懂似的 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怜的女儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,造成那场事故的人就是目标人物牧村达彦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司机也已经在那场事故中死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鱼肉山芋饼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菊理要香肠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我调查了那个牧村达彦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到对方却是个极其普通的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都不像是能招人怨恨的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 不管怎么调查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都查不出牧村和贵八之间的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕两个人根本就不认识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说久住贵八\N要让素未谋面的牧村达彦下地狱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,油炸豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菊理要香肠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我一直想问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要扮卖关东煮的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是调查本部所在的狛江泽警署前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事件发生后只过了三个月…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 别推我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里摆个摊 警察啊传媒的就会来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在收集情报这方面是再好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么成果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个嘛 委托人的信息完全收集不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过却拿到一些很有意思的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连续杀人魔事件的调查资料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干的不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 这是警长忘在这儿的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛筋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菊理要香肠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛筋和香肠对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V字手势
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和平？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是数字2
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什么意图
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是犯人杀人之后刻意做出的手势
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 凶器是竹制的签状物件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.89,0:12:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接写竹签不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竹签
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香肠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菊理也要香肠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 刚才给小姐的已经是最后一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久住先生 无须告诉您检查结果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您还是住院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还能活多久
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再病倒的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了 医生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久住先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 又来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见 爸爸走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜八先生好像也得病了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是刽子手的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.21,0:14:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁来救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:14:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连续杀人魔事件的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你并不吃惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜过是可能你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惨剧发生在周日下午
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久住喜八先生的店铺兼住宅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一辆卡车撞上来后 燃起熊熊大火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司机当场死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久住先生的妻子和7岁的长子也死于这场意外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事故中保住性命的久住先生的长女椿小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 事件的被害人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时吵吵着的 屎壳郎一样起哄的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以把被害人的手都…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三个月前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在小椿入住的那家医院里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做了次住院综合体检
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后 发现肺部有阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受精密检查的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来也为时已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.47,0:16:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直坚信总有一天小椿能苏醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来是难以如愿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我所剩无几的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用来除掉那群蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也实在不走运
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明已经知道了下一个人的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的日子却也不长久了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且还被看到了脸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.77,0:16:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会被抓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不论哪个我都难以报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 就把最后的愿望托付给这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 原来是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 原来你就是地狱少女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就解开这根红线
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解开绳线
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就与我正式缔结了契约
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨的对象立即会被放逐到地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨若已消除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自身也要付出代价
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缔结契约以后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.38,0:18:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂亦将堕入地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我犯了那么大的罪是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就有下地狱的准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个代价另计
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下地狱不过是你让别人下地狱的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己所犯的罪和我毫不相干
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.94,0:18:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说杀人的罪过 到地狱还要付出另外的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我不在这儿和你缔结契约也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我心甘情愿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过如此苟延残喘的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也能做为代价啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨已闻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请您说两句
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您确实看到了连续杀人事件的犯人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 亲眼所见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别推我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巡查先生 救…救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁来救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.27,0:20:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们听见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷途于黑暗中的可悲阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤害 鄙视他人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.47,0:20:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于罪恶的孽魂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来死一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.49,0:20:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.70,0:20:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ok
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这份怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将流向地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.47,0:21:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你想怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.15,0:21:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连续杀人魔事件的犯人是疑犯久住喜八
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久住先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做出您是凶手的证词的牧村达彦先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说从昨晚起下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问您知道什么情况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就能瞑目了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.02,0:21:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久住先生 久住先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:21:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小椿 小椿醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小…小椿 小椿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.73,0:22:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小椿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久住先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冤冤相报何时了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.62,0:22:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小椿是杀人犯的女儿这点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜八也会感到负罪的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.08,0:22:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是小姐所说的代价另计吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.57,0:22:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也太过悲惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.03,0:22:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 为什么他女儿突然醒过来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.65,0:22:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生也没有料到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.91,0:22:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小椿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:23:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的怨恨 替你消除
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.61,0:24:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.97,0:24:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红林拓真
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.38,0:24:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.76,0:24:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想把他碎尸万段吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.77,0:24:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人绝对就是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.55,0:24:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为那家伙我家人才…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.56,0:24:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下地狱吧下地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.04,0:24:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送他下地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.81,0:24:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.95,0:24:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.72,0:24:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨已听取咯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.71,0:24:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.95,0:24:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,静寂的湖畔
